BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aKZVMH31QkpwPe4nkOAIY
SUMMARY:SP 201: Poster Printing
DTSTAMP:20260325T060832Z
DTSTART:20260509T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Show posters\, art prints\, and flat-stock paper print projects
	 galore! In this hands-on workshop\, students will build on the basics of 
	paper-based printing by practicing with a two-color design\, specifically 
	designed for the Poster Printing class. Learn concepts such as the basics 
	of color separation\, print registration\, proper equipment use\, and help
	ful tips to successfully run a series of prints in a DIY or professional s
	tudio.\n\nPre-requisites: Students must complete Screenprint 101 before at
	tending this class.\n\nThe Vera Project does not provide refunds nor resch
	edule tickets for other class dates.\n\nhttps://link.dice.fm/z38cc4b8893a\
	n\nFrom The Vera Project
